The Unreal Engine 4 (UE4) Plugin system allows anyone to add a wide range of new functionality to UE4 without the need to recompile and distribute the entire engine. In the following How - To we will recreate the Lens Distortion global shader plugin to demonstrate how you would go about implementing a global shader that is controllable via Blueprints.

